
Core functionality:
  ☐ Create a task (title and categories)
  ☐ Save task in localStorage
  ☐ Edit a task (title and categories)
  ☐ Delete a task (from localStorage)
  ☐ Mark a task as completed (status)

Additional Features:
  ☐ Filter tasks by status (all, completed, pending)
  ☐ Filter tasks by categories
  ☐ Reorder tasks via drag-and-drop
  ☐ Search for tasks by keywords
  ☐ Dark/light mode